 i suggested boiled milk or tea and the housekeeper received instructions to prepare some come i reflected his selfishness may contribute to his comfort he perceives his delicate constitution and the necessity of treating him tolerably console mr edgar by acquainting him with the turn humour has taken having no excuse for lingering longer i slipped out while linton was engaged in timidly rebuilding the advances of a friendly sheepdog but he was too much on the alert to be cheated as i closed the door i heard a cry and a frantic repetition of the words 
 leave me not stay here not stay here 
 then the latch was raised and fell they did not suffer him to come forth i mounted minny and urged her to a trot and so my brief guardianship ended 
 
 
 
