 and then through the fog that was drowning him he thought he saw a silvery light growing brighter and brighter he felt himself fall forward onto the grass facedown too weak to move sick and shaking harry opened his eyes the dementor must have released him the blinding light was illuminating the grass around himthe screaming had stopped the cold was ebbing away 
 
 something was driving the dementors back it was circling around him and black and hermione they were leaving 
 
